{
  "video_id": "NlYJQ0psZYA",
  "title": "Walk the earth ... my 17-year vow of silence | John Francis",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12160.0,
      "end_time": 55160.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 55160.0,
      "end_time": 61160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 61160.0,
      "end_time": 64160.0,
      "text": "Thank you for being here."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 64160.0,
      "end_time": 72160.0,
      "text": "And I say \"thank you for being here\" because I was silent for 17 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 72160.0,
      "end_time": 76160.0,
      "text": "And the first words that I spoke were in Washington, D.C.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 76160.0,
      "end_time": 78160.0,
      "text": "on the 20th anniversary of Earth Day."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 78160.0,
      "end_time": 83160.0,
      "text": "And my family and friends had gathered there to hear me speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 83160.0,
      "end_time": 87160.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Thank you for being here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 87160.0,
      "end_time": 88160.0,
      "text": "My mother, out in the audience, she jumped up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 88160.0,
      "end_time": 91160.0,
      "text": "\"Hallelujah, Johnny’s talking!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 91160.0,
      "end_time": 93160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 93160.0,
      "end_time": 95160.0,
      "text": "Imagine if you were quiet for 17 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 95160.0,
      "end_time": 99160.0,
      "text": "and your mother was out in the audience, say."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 99160.0,
      "end_time": 102160.0,
      "text": "My dad said to me, \"That’s one\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 102160.0,
      "end_time": 105160.0,
      "text": "I’ll explain that."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 105160.0,
      "end_time": 110160.0,
      "text": "But I turned around because I didn’t recognize where my voice was coming from."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 110160.0,
      "end_time": 113160.0,
      "text": "I hadn’t heard my voice in 17 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 113160.0,
      "end_time": 115160.0,
      "text": "so I turned around and I looked and I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 115160.0,
      "end_time": 119160.0,
      "text": "\"God, who&#39;s saying what I’m thinking?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 119160.0,
      "end_time": 124160.0,
      "text": "And then I realized it was me, you know, and I kind of laughed."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 124160.0,
      "end_time": 129160.0,
      "text": "And I could see my father: \"Yeah, he really is crazy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 129160.0,
      "end_time": 133160.0,
      "text": "Well, I want to take you on this journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 133160.0,
      "end_time": 136160.0,
      "text": "And the journey, I believe, is a metaphor for all of our journeys."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 136160.0,
      "end_time": 140160.0,
      "text": "Even though this one is kind of unusual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 140160.0,
      "end_time": 145160.0,
      "text": "I want you to think about your own journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 145160.0,
      "end_time": 149160.0,
      "text": "My journey began in 1971"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 149160.0,
      "end_time": 155160.0,
      "text": "when I witnessed two oil tankers collide beneath the Golden Gate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 155160.0,
      "end_time": 159160.0,
      "text": "and a half a million gallons of oil spilled into the bay."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 159160.0,
      "end_time": 163160.0,
      "text": "It disturbed me so much"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 163160.0,
      "end_time": 169160.0,
      "text": "that I decided that I was going to give up riding and driving in motorized vehicles."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 170160.0,
      "end_time": 173160.0,
      "text": "That’s a big thing in California."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 173160.0,
      "end_time": 179160.0,
      "text": "And it was a big thing in my little community of Point Reyes Station"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 179160.0,
      "end_time": 181160.0,
      "text": "in Inverness, California, because there were only"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 181160.0,
      "end_time": 187160.0,
      "text": "about 350 people there in the winter – this was back in &#39;71 now."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 187160.0,
      "end_time": 192160.0,
      "text": "And so when I came in and I started walking around, people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 192160.0,
      "end_time": 194160.0,
      "text": "they just knew what was going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 194160.0,
      "end_time": 196160.0,
      "text": "And people would drive up next to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 196160.0,
      "end_time": 198160.0,
      "text": "and say, \"John, what are you doing?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 198160.0,
      "end_time": 202160.0,
      "text": "And I’d say, \"Well, I’m walking for the environment.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 202160.0,
      "end_time": 206160.0,
      "text": "And they said, \"No, you’re walking to make us look bad, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 206160.0,
      "end_time": 208160.0,
      "text": "You’re walking to make us feel bad.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 208160.0,
      "end_time": 210160.0,
      "text": "And maybe there was some truth to that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 210160.0,
      "end_time": 215160.0,
      "text": "because I thought that if I started walking, everyone would follow."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 215160.0,
      "end_time": 217160.0,
      "text": "Because of the oil, everybody talked about the polllution."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 217160.0,
      "end_time": 224160.0,
      "text": "And so I argued with people about that, I argued and I argued."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 224160.0,
      "end_time": 226160.0,
      "text": "I called my parents up."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 226160.0,
      "end_time": 228160.0,
      "text": "I said, \"I’ve given up riding and driving in cars.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 228160.0,
      "end_time": 231160.0,
      "text": "My dad said, \"Why didn’t you do that when you were 16?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 231160.0,
      "end_time": 233160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 233160.0,
      "end_time": 234160.0,
      "text": "I didn’t know about the environment then."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 234160.0,
      "end_time": 236160.0,
      "text": "They’re back in Philadelphia."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 236160.0,
      "end_time": 240160.0,
      "text": "And so I told my mother, \"I’m happy though, I’m really happy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 240160.0,
      "end_time": 243160.0,
      "text": "She said, \"If you were happy, son, you wouldn’t have to say it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 243160.0,
      "end_time": 246160.0,
      "text": "Mothers are like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 246160.0,
      "end_time": 254160.0,
      "text": "And so, on my 27th birthday I decided, because I argued so much"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 254160.0,
      "end_time": 260159.0,
      "text": "and I talk so much, that I was going to stop speaking"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 260160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264160.0,
      "text": "for just one day -- one day -- to give it a rest."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 264160.0,
      "end_time": 267160.0,
      "text": "And so I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 267160.0,
      "end_time": 270160.0,
      "text": "I got up in the morning and I didn’t say a word."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 270160.0,
      "end_time": 273160.0,
      "text": "And I have to tell you, it was a very moving experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 273160.0,
      "end_time": 280160.0,
      "text": "because for the first time, I began listening -- in a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 280160.0,
      "end_time": 284160.0,
      "text": "And what I heard, it kind of disturbed me."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 284160.0,
      "end_time": 287160.0,
      "text": "Because what I used to do, when I thought I was listening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 287160.0,
      "end_time": 290160.0,
      "text": "was I would listen just enough to hear what people had to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 290160.0,
      "end_time": 295160.0,
      "text": "and think that I could -- I knew what they were going to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 295160.0,
      "end_time": 297160.0,
      "text": "and so I stopped listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 297160.0,
      "end_time": 300160.0,
      "text": "And in my mind, I just kind of raced ahead"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 300160.0,
      "end_time": 302160.0,
      "text": "and thought of what I was going to say back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 302160.0,
      "end_time": 304160.0,
      "text": "while they were still finishing up."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 304160.0,
      "end_time": 306160.0,
      "text": "And then I would launch in."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 306160.0,
      "end_time": 310160.0,
      "text": "Well, that just ended communication."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 310160.0,
      "end_time": 312160.0,
      "text": "So on this first day I actually listened."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 312160.0,
      "end_time": 314160.0,
      "text": "And it was very sad for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 314160.0,
      "end_time": 320160.0,
      "text": "because I realized that for those many years I had not been learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 320160.0,
      "end_time": 322160.0,
      "text": "I was 27. I thought I knew everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 325160.0,
      "end_time": 327160.0,
      "text": "I didn’t."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 327160.0,
      "end_time": 331160.0,
      "text": "And so I decided I’d better do this for another day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 331160.0,
      "end_time": 335160.0,
      "text": "and another day, and another day until finally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 335160.0,
      "end_time": 338160.0,
      "text": "I promised myself for a year I would keep quiet"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 338160.0,
      "end_time": 342160.0,
      "text": "because I started learning more and more and I needed to learn more."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 342160.0,
      "end_time": 344160.0,
      "text": "So for a year I said I would keep quiet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 344160.0,
      "end_time": 348160.0,
      "text": "and then on my birthday I would reassess what I had learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 348160.0,
      "end_time": 350160.0,
      "text": "and maybe I would talk again."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 350160.0,
      "end_time": 353160.0,
      "text": "Well, that lasted 17 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 354160.0,
      "end_time": 360160.0,
      "text": "Now during that time -- those 17 years -- I walked and I played the banjo"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 360160.0,
      "end_time": 365160.0,
      "text": "and I painted and I wrote in my journal, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 365160.0,
      "end_time": 370160.0,
      "text": "I tried to study the environment by reading books."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 370160.0,
      "end_time": 374160.0,
      "text": "And I decided that I was going to go to school. So I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 374160.0,
      "end_time": 376160.0,
      "text": "I walked up to Ashland, Oregon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 376160.0,
      "end_time": 381160.0,
      "text": "where they were offering an environmental studies degree."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 381160.0,
      "end_time": 383160.0,
      "text": "It’s only 500 miles."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 383160.0,
      "end_time": 387160.0,
      "text": "And I went into the Registrar’s office and --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 392160.0,
      "end_time": 394160.0,
      "text": "\"What, what, what?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 394160.0,
      "end_time": 397160.0,
      "text": "I had a newspaper clipping."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 397160.0,
      "end_time": 399160.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, so you really want to go to school here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 399160.0,
      "end_time": 401160.0,
      "text": "You don’t …?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 401160.0,
      "end_time": 404160.0,
      "text": "We have a special program for you.\" They did."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 404160.0,
      "end_time": 409160.0,
      "text": "And in those two years, I graduated with my first degree -- a bachelor’s degree."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 409160.0,
      "end_time": 412160.0,
      "text": "And my father came out, he was so proud."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 412160.0,
      "end_time": 415160.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Listen, we’re really proud of you son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 415160.0,
      "end_time": 417160.0,
      "text": "but what are you going to do with a bachelor’s degree?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 417160.0,
      "end_time": 419160.0,
      "text": "You don’t ride in cars, you don’t talk --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 419160.0,
      "end_time": 421160.0,
      "text": "you’re going to have to do those things.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 421160.0,
      "end_time": 423160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 423160.0,
      "end_time": 425160.0,
      "text": "I hunched my shoulder, I picked my backpack up again"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 425160.0,
      "end_time": 427160.0,
      "text": "and I started walking."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 429160.0,
      "end_time": 434160.0,
      "text": "I walked all the way up to Port Townsend, Washington, where I built a wooden boat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 434160.0,
      "end_time": 437160.0,
      "text": "rode it across Puget Sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 437160.0,
      "end_time": 442160.0,
      "text": "and walked across Washington [to] Idaho and down to Missoula, Montana."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 442160.0,
      "end_time": 446160.0,
      "text": "I had written the University of Montana two years earlier"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 446160.0,
      "end_time": 449160.0,
      "text": "and said I&#39;d like to go to school there."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 449160.0,
      "end_time": 452160.0,
      "text": "I said I&#39;d be there in about two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 452160.0,
      "end_time": 454160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 454160.0,
      "end_time": 457160.0,
      "text": "And I was there. I showed up in two years and they --"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 457160.0,
      "end_time": 459160.0,
      "text": "I tell this story because they really helped me."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 459160.0,
      "end_time": 461160.0,
      "text": "There are two stories in Montana."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 463160.0,
      "end_time": 466160.0,
      "text": "The first story is I didn’t have any money -- that’s a sign I used a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 466160.0,
      "end_time": 469160.0,
      "text": "And they said,\"Don&#39;t worry about that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 469160.0,
      "end_time": 472160.0,
      "text": "The director of the program said, \"Come back tomorrow.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 472160.0,
      "end_time": 474160.0,
      "text": "He gave me 150 dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 474160.0,
      "end_time": 477160.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"Register for one credit."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 477160.0,
      "end_time": 479160.0,
      "text": "You’re going to go to South America, aren’t you?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 479160.0,
      "end_time": 481160.0,
      "text": "And I said --"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 481160.0,
      "end_time": 485160.0,
      "text": "Rivers and lakes, the hydrological systems, South America."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 485160.0,
      "end_time": 488160.0,
      "text": "So I did that."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 488160.0,
      "end_time": 490160.0,
      "text": "He came back; he said to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 490160.0,
      "end_time": 494160.0,
      "text": "\"OK John, now that you&#39;ve registered for that one credit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 494160.0,
      "end_time": 497160.0,
      "text": "you can have a key to an office, you can matriculate --"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 497160.0,
      "end_time": 499160.0,
      "text": "you’re matriculating, so you can use the library."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 499160.0,
      "end_time": 500160.0,
      "text": "And what we’re going to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 500160.0,
      "end_time": 506160.0,
      "text": "is, we’re going to have all of the professors allow you to go to class."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 506160.0,
      "end_time": 508160.0,
      "text": "They’re going to save your grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 508160.0,
      "end_time": 510160.0,
      "text": "and when we figure out how to get you the rest of the money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 510160.0,
      "end_time": 517160.0,
      "text": "then you can register for that class and they’ll give you the grade.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 517159.0,
      "end_time": 520159.0,
      "text": "Wow, they don’t do that in graduate schools, I don’t think."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 520159.0,
      "end_time": 524159.0,
      "text": "But I use that story because they really wanted to help me."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 524159.0,
      "end_time": 527160.0,
      "text": "They saw that I was really interested in the environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 527160.0,
      "end_time": 529160.0,
      "text": "and they really wanted to help me along the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 529160.0,
      "end_time": 534160.0,
      "text": "And during that time, I actually taught classes without speaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 534160.0,
      "end_time": 537160.0,
      "text": "I had 13 students when I first walked into the class."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 537160.0,
      "end_time": 543160.0,
      "text": "I explained, with a friend who could interpret my sign language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 543160.0,
      "end_time": 545160.0,
      "text": "that I was John Francis, I was walking around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 545160.0,
      "end_time": 546160.0,
      "text": "I didn’t talk and this was the last time"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 546160.0,
      "end_time": 549160.0,
      "text": "this person’s going to be here interpreting for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 549160.0,
      "end_time": 552160.0,
      "text": "All the students sat around and they went ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 552160.0,
      "end_time": 557160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 557160.0,
      "end_time": 559160.0,
      "text": "I could see they were looking for the schedule,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 559160.0,
      "end_time": 561160.0,
      "text": "to see when they could get out."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 561160.0,
      "end_time": 565160.0,
      "text": "They had to take that class with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 565160.0,
      "end_time": 568160.0,
      "text": "Two weeks later, everyone was trying to get into our class."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 568160.0,
      "end_time": 572160.0,
      "text": "And I learned in that class -- because I would do things like this ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 572160.0,
      "end_time": 574160.0,
      "text": "and they were all gathered around, going, \"What&#39;s he trying to say?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 574160.0,
      "end_time": 579160.0,
      "text": "\"I don&#39;t know, I think he&#39;s talking about clear cutting.\" \"Yeah, clear cutting.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 579160.0,
      "end_time": 582160.0,
      "text": "\"No, no, no, that&#39;s not clear cutting, that’s -- he&#39;s using a handsaw.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 583160.0,
      "end_time": 586160.0,
      "text": "\"Well, you can’t clearcut with a ...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 586160.0,
      "end_time": 588160.0,
      "text": "\"Yes, you can clear cut ...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 588160.0,
      "end_time": 590160.0,
      "text": "\"No, I think he’s talking about selective forestry.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 590160.0,
      "end_time": 594160.0,
      "text": "Now this was a discussion class and we were having a discussion."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 594160.0,
      "end_time": 597160.0,
      "text": "I just backed out of that, you know, and I just kind of kept the fists from flying."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 597160.0,
      "end_time": 601160.0,
      "text": "But what I learned was that sometimes I would make a sign"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 601160.0,
      "end_time": 605160.0,
      "text": "and they said things that I absolutely did not mean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 605160.0,
      "end_time": 607160.0,
      "text": "but I should have."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 607160.0,
      "end_time": 612160.0,
      "text": "And so what came to me is, if you were a teacher"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 612160.0,
      "end_time": 615160.0,
      "text": "and you were teaching, if you weren’t learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 615160.0,
      "end_time": 617160.0,
      "text": "you probably weren’t teaching very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 617160.0,
      "end_time": 619160.0,
      "text": "And so I went on."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 619160.0,
      "end_time": 621160.0,
      "text": "My dad came out to see me graduate"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 621160.0,
      "end_time": 623160.0,
      "text": "and, you know, I did the deal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 623160.0,
      "end_time": 625160.0,
      "text": "and my father said, \"We’re really proud of you son, but ... \""
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 625160.0,
      "end_time": 627160.0,
      "text": "You know what went on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 627160.0,
      "end_time": 630160.0,
      "text": "he said, \"You’ve got to start riding and driving and start talking."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 630160.0,
      "end_time": 632160.0,
      "text": "What are you going to do with a master’s degree?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 632160.0,
      "end_time": 634160.0,
      "text": "I hunched my shoulder, I got my backpack"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 634160.0,
      "end_time": 636160.0,
      "text": "and I went on to the University of Wisconsin."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 637160.0,
      "end_time": 642160.0,
      "text": "I spent two years there writing on oil spills."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 642160.0,
      "end_time": 644160.0,
      "text": "No one was interested in oil spills."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 644160.0,
      "end_time": 646160.0,
      "text": "But something happened --"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 647160.0,
      "end_time": 649160.0,
      "text": "Exxon Valdez."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 650160.0,
      "end_time": 654160.0,
      "text": "And I was the only one in the United States writing on oil spills."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 654160.0,
      "end_time": 656160.0,
      "text": "My dad came out again."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 656160.0,
      "end_time": 658160.0,
      "text": "He said, \"I don&#39;t know how you do this, son --"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 658160.0,
      "end_time": 661160.0,
      "text": "I mean, you don&#39;t ride in cars, you don’t talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 661160.0,
      "end_time": 663160.0,
      "text": "My sister said maybe I should leave you alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 663160.0,
      "end_time": 665160.0,
      "text": "because you seem to be doing a lot better"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 665160.0,
      "end_time": 667160.0,
      "text": "when you’re not saying anything.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 667160.0,
      "end_time": 670160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 670160.0,
      "end_time": 672160.0,
      "text": "Well, I put on my backpack again."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 672160.0,
      "end_time": 674160.0,
      "text": "I put my banjo on and I walked all the way to the East Coast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 674160.0,
      "end_time": 676160.0,
      "text": "put my foot in the Atlantic Ocean --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 676160.0,
      "end_time": 680160.0,
      "text": "it was seven years and one day it took me to walk across the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 682160.0,
      "end_time": 687160.0,
      "text": "And on Earth Day, 1990 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 687160.0,
      "end_time": 690160.0,
      "text": "the 20th anniversary of Earth Day -- that’s when I began to speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 690160.0,
      "end_time": 692160.0,
      "text": "And that’s why I said, \"Thank you for being here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 692160.0,
      "end_time": 696160.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s sort of like that tree in the forest falling;"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 696160.0,
      "end_time": 699160.0,
      "text": "and if there&#39;s no one there to hear, does it really make a sound?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 699160.0,
      "end_time": 702160.0,
      "text": "And I’m thanking you, and I&#39;m thanking my family"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 702160.0,
      "end_time": 704160.0,
      "text": "because they had come to hear me speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 704160.0,
      "end_time": 707160.0,
      "text": "And that’s communication."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 707160.0,
      "end_time": 713160.0,
      "text": "And they also taught me about listening -- that they listened to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 713160.0,
      "end_time": 717160.0,
      "text": "And it’s one of those things that came out of the silence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 717160.0,
      "end_time": 719160.0,
      "text": "the listening to each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 719160.0,
      "end_time": 721160.0,
      "text": "Really, very important --"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 721160.0,
      "end_time": 724160.0,
      "text": "we need to listen to each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 724160.0,
      "end_time": 726160.0,
      "text": "Well, my journey kept going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 726160.0,
      "end_time": 729160.0,
      "text": "My dad said, \"That’s one,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 729160.0,
      "end_time": 732160.0,
      "text": "and I still didn’t let that go."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 732160.0,
      "end_time": 735160.0,
      "text": "I worked for the Coastguard, was made a U.N. Goodwill Ambassador."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 735160.0,
      "end_time": 738160.0,
      "text": "I wrote regulations for the United States --"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 738160.0,
      "end_time": 740160.0,
      "text": "I mean, I wrote oil spill regulations."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 740160.0,
      "end_time": 744160.0,
      "text": "20 years ago, if someone had said to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 744160.0,
      "end_time": 747160.0,
      "text": "\"John, do you really want to make a difference?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 747160.0,
      "end_time": 748160.0,
      "text": "\"Yeah, I want to make a difference.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 748160.0,
      "end_time": 750160.0,
      "text": "He said, \"You just start walking east;"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 750160.0,
      "end_time": 753160.0,
      "text": "get out of your car and just start walking east.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 753160.0,
      "end_time": 757160.0,
      "text": "And as I walked off a little bit, they&#39;d say, \"Yeah, and shut up, too.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 757160.0,
      "end_time": 760160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 760160.0,
      "end_time": 762160.0,
      "text": "\"You’re going to make a difference, buddy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 762160.0,
      "end_time": 765160.0,
      "text": "How could that be, how could that be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 765160.0,
      "end_time": 769160.0,
      "text": "How could doing such a simple thing like walking and not talking"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 769160.0,
      "end_time": 771160.0,
      "text": "make a difference?"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 771160.0,
      "end_time": 775160.0,
      "text": "Well, my time at the Coast Guard was a really good time."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 775160.0,
      "end_time": 778160.0,
      "text": "And after that -- I only worked one year --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 778160.0,
      "end_time": 782160.0,
      "text": "I said, \"That&#39;s enough. One year&#39;s enough for me to do that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 782160.0,
      "end_time": 785160.0,
      "text": "I got on a sailboat and I sailed down to the Caribbean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 785160.0,
      "end_time": 792160.0,
      "text": "and walked through all of the islands, and to Venezuela."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 792160.0,
      "end_time": 796160.0,
      "text": "And you know, I forgot the most important thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 796160.0,
      "end_time": 801160.0,
      "text": "which is why I started talking, which I have to tell you."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 801160.0,
      "end_time": 806160.0,
      "text": "I started talking because I had studied environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 806160.0,
      "end_time": 810160.0,
      "text": "I’d studied environment at this formal level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 810160.0,
      "end_time": 812160.0,
      "text": "but there was this informal level."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 812160.0,
      "end_time": 815160.0,
      "text": "And the informal level --"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 815160.0,
      "end_time": 821160.0,
      "text": "I learned about people, and what we do and how we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 821160.0,
      "end_time": 824160.0,
      "text": "And environment changed from just being about trees and birds"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 824160.0,
      "end_time": 830160.0,
      "text": "and endangered species to being about how we treated each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 830160.0,
      "end_time": 832160.0,
      "text": "Because if we are the environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 832160.0,
      "end_time": 834160.0,
      "text": "then all we need to do is look around us"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 834160.0,
      "end_time": 839160.0,
      "text": "and see how we treat ourselves and how we treat each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 839160.0,
      "end_time": 843160.0,
      "text": "And so that’s the message that I had."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 843160.0,
      "end_time": 845160.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Well, I&#39;m going to have to spread that message.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 845160.0,
      "end_time": 849160.0,
      "text": "And I got in my sailboat, sailed all the way through the Caribbean --"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 849160.0,
      "end_time": 853160.0,
      "text": "it wasn&#39;t really my sailboat, I kind of worked on that boat --"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 853160.0,
      "end_time": 857160.0,
      "text": "got to Venezuela and I started walking."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 857160.0,
      "end_time": 860160.0,
      "text": "This is the last part of this story, because it’s how I got here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 860160.0,
      "end_time": 863160.0,
      "text": "because I still didn&#39;t ride in motorized vehicles."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 863160.0,
      "end_time": 870160.0,
      "text": "I was walking through El Dorado -- it&#39;s a prison town, famous prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 870160.0,
      "end_time": 875160.0,
      "text": "or infamous prison -- in Venezuela, and I don’t know what possessed me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 875160.0,
      "end_time": 877160.0,
      "text": "because this was not like me."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 877160.0,
      "end_time": 884160.0,
      "text": "There I am, walking past the guard gate and the guard stops and says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 884160.0,
      "end_time": 889160.0,
      "text": "\"Pasaporte, pasaporte,\" and with an M16 pointed at me."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 889160.0,
      "end_time": 893160.0,
      "text": "And I looked at him and I said, \"Passport, huh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 893160.0,
      "end_time": 896160.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t need to show you my passport. It’s in the back of my pack."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 896160.0,
      "end_time": 902160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m Dr. Francis; I&#39;m a U.N. Ambassador and I&#39;m walking around the world.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 902160.0,
      "end_time": 904160.0,
      "text": "And I started walking off."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 904160.0,
      "end_time": 906160.0,
      "text": "What possessed me to say this thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 909160.0,
      "end_time": 911160.0,
      "text": "The road turned into the jungle."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 911160.0,
      "end_time": 913160.0,
      "text": "I didn’t get shot."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 913160.0,
      "end_time": 917160.0,
      "text": "And I got to -- I start saying, \"Free at last --"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 917160.0,
      "end_time": 920160.0,
      "text": "thank God Almighty, I’m free at last.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 924160.0,
      "end_time": 927160.0,
      "text": "\"What was that about,\" I’m saying. What was that about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 927160.0,
      "end_time": 935160.0,
      "text": "It took me 100 miles to figure out that, in my heart, in me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 935160.0,
      "end_time": 938160.0,
      "text": "I had become a prisoner."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 938160.0,
      "end_time": 942160.0,
      "text": "I was a prisoner and I needed to escape."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 942160.0,
      "end_time": 948160.0,
      "text": "The prison that I was in was the fact that I did not drive"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 948160.0,
      "end_time": 950160.0,
      "text": "or use motorized vehicles."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 950160.0,
      "end_time": 952160.0,
      "text": "Now how could that be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 952160.0,
      "end_time": 956160.0,
      "text": "Because when I started, it seemed very appropriate to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 956160.0,
      "end_time": 958160.0,
      "text": "not to use motorized vehicles."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 958160.0,
      "end_time": 960160.0,
      "text": "But the thing that was different"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 960160.0,
      "end_time": 963160.0,
      "text": "was that every birthday, I asked myself about silence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 963160.0,
      "end_time": 971160.0,
      "text": "but I never asked myself about my decision to just use my feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 971160.0,
      "end_time": 974160.0,
      "text": "I had no idea I was going to become a U.N. Ambassador."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 974160.0,
      "end_time": 978160.0,
      "text": "I had no idea I would have a Ph.D."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 978160.0,
      "end_time": 984160.0,
      "text": "And so I realized that I had a responsibility to more than just me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 984160.0,
      "end_time": 986160.0,
      "text": "and that I was going to have to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 986160.0,
      "end_time": 989160.0,
      "text": "You know, we can do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 989160.0,
      "end_time": 991160.0,
      "text": "I was going to have to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 991160.0,
      "end_time": 993160.0,
      "text": "And I was afraid to change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 993160.0,
      "end_time": 996160.0,
      "text": "because I was so used to the guy who only just walked."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 996160.0,
      "end_time": 1002160.0,
      "text": "I was so used to that person that I didn’t want to stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1002160.0,
      "end_time": 1005160.0,
      "text": "I didn’t know who I would be if I changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1005160.0,
      "end_time": 1008160.0,
      "text": "But I know I needed to."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1008160.0,
      "end_time": 1012160.0,
      "text": "I know I needed to change, because it would be the only way"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1012160.0,
      "end_time": 1014160.0,
      "text": "that I could be here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1016160.0,
      "end_time": 1019160.0,
      "text": "And I know that a lot of times"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1019160.0,
      "end_time": 1023160.0,
      "text": "we find ourselves in this wonderful place where we’ve gotten to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1023160.0,
      "end_time": 1026159.0,
      "text": "but there’s another place for us to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1026160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1032160.0000000001,
      "text": "And we kind of have to leave behind the security of who we’ve become,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1032160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1039160.0000000001,
      "text": "and go to the place of who we are becoming."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1039160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1048160.0000000001,
      "text": "And so, I want to encourage you to go to that next place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1048160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1053160.0,
      "text": "to let yourself out of any prison that you might find yourself in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1053160.0,
      "end_time": 1061160.0,
      "text": "as comfortable as it may be, because we have to do something now."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1061160.0,
      "end_time": 1064160.0,
      "text": "We have to change now."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1067160.0,
      "end_time": 1072160.0,
      "text": "As our former Vice President said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1072160.0,
      "end_time": 1074160.0,
      "text": "we have to become activists."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1076160.0,
      "end_time": 1080160.0,
      "text": "So if my voice can touch you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1080160.0,
      "end_time": 1084160.0,
      "text": "if my actions can touch you, if my being here can touch you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1084160.0,
      "end_time": 1086160.0,
      "text": "please let it be."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1086160.0,
      "end_time": 1091160.0,
      "text": "And I know that all of you have touched me"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1091160.0,
      "end_time": 1094160.0,
      "text": "while I’ve been here."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1096160.0,
      "end_time": 1099160.0,
      "text": "So, let’s go out into the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1099160.0,
      "end_time": 1102160.0,
      "text": "and take this caring, this love, this respect"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1102160.0,
      "end_time": 1107160.0,
      "text": "that we’ve shown each other right here at TED,"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1107160.0,
      "end_time": 1109160.0,
      "text": "and take this out into the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1109160.0,
      "end_time": 1114160.0,
      "text": "Because we are the environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1114160.0,
      "end_time": 1117160.0,
      "text": "and how we treat each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1117160.0,
      "end_time": 1122160.0,
      "text": "is really how we’re going to treat the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1122160.0,
      "end_time": 1126160.0,
      "text": "So I want to thank you for being here"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1126160.0,
      "end_time": 1131160.0,
      "text": "and I want to end this in five seconds of silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1139160.0,
      "end_time": 1141160.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1141160.0,
      "end_time": 1159160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}